> **⚠️ `/Add Multiple Languages` WARNING**: This command frequently causes translation contamination and "fix loop" spirals. Multiple users have spent $100–$250+ trying to fix broken multi-language apps. Only use for very simple apps. For serious apps, build the full primary-language version first, then manually add translations one language at a time using `@` commands scoped to the translation files.

